&lt;h3 class=&quot;text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold&quot;&gt;About Ascend&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;Ascend (formerly FlyFlat) is a membership-based travel concierge service that delivers 24/7 end-to-end journey management for frequent travelers and corporate teams. Members save an average of 35% on business and first-class flights and reclaim hours of planning time, communicating directly with a dedicated human concierge team via WhatsApp to book flights, hotels, and ground transport, with proactive disruption management throughout the journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;The combination of white-glove service and proprietary technology is what makes the model work—and that&#39;s where this role sits. We&#39;re scaling the platform, the team, and the surface area of what a small engineering org can credibly own, including how AI-assisted development reshapes that ceiling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold&quot;&gt;The Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;As a Senior Python Backend Developer at Ascend, you&#39;ll lead development of our Python-based web applications using Django and FastAPI. You&#39;ll architect scalable solutions, implement best practices, and help shape our technical direction while working with modern cloud infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;Beyond traditional engineering, you&#39;ll play a meaningful role in how Ascend adopts AI-assisted development—both inside Engineering and in the tooling, standards, and guardrails we extend to the rest of the organization. We expect AI to be a first-class part of how our team ships, reviews, and operates, and we want someone who has opinions on what that should look like.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;This is a remote role paying $3500 - $4500 per month, DOE.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold&quot;&gt;Who You Are&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;You&#39;re an experienced developer with deep Python expertise and a passion for building high-performance web applications. You combine technical excellence with pragmatic problem-solving and enjoy the challenges of a growing company. You&#39;re also fluent in modern AI-augmented development: you know when to reach for AI tools, where they fall short, and how to build the structures (prompts, skills, review processes, evaluation harnesses, access controls) that let a team use them productively and safely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h3&gt;
