&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Lead development of features using Django and FastAPI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Architect and implement scalable web applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Establish technical standards for our Python codebase, including standards for AI-assisted contributions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Optimize our cloud infrastructure (Railway, with selective AWS usage)&lt;/li&gt;
